    	<h1 class="span12 ">Public History</h1>
	

    
    	<div class="span12"><p>Concordiaâ¬"s History Department is unique in Canada in terms of the wealth of resources that it possesses to study the use of history in the public sphere and to produce tools to communicate the past to the larger public.</p>
